I"Â<h2 id="learning-objectives">Learning Objectives</h2>

<p>In this module we will continue talking about distributed generation from a grid integration perspective. The learning outcomes of this module are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Understanding the challenges from a distribution grid operation perspective;</li>
  <li>Understanding the challenges from a DG optimization perspective - siting and sizing, planning;</li>
  <li>Overview of the Solar Industry outlook in U.S. and rest of the world;</li>
  <li>Understanding the duck curve, renewable curtailment and discussing ways to flatten the curve.</li>
</ul>

